<L>__{interior yasnaya polyana. entry way stairs. day.}
<A>__{valentin stands in the entry way, waiting. he looks lost.}
<C>__{valentin}
<D>__{hello...hello...}
<C>__{voice }
<D>__{you're the new secretary.}
<A>__{he looks up to see sasha examining him from the landing above.}
<C>__{sasha}
<D>__{papa's out. you can wait in the library. ivan will show you up.}
<A>__{she disappears. he hears a door close. he notices a surly house servant, ivan, who, inexplicably, leads a goat through the house. he points upstairs and walks away.}
